  <title>PART-TIME TEACHING ASSISTANTS (4 POSITIONS)- CIVIL ENGINEERING</title>
  <link>https://www.ub.bw/connect/job-opportunities/part-time-teaching-assistants-4-positions-civil-engineering</link>
  <description>&lt;span class="field field--name-title field--type-string field--label-hidden"&gt;PART-TIME TEACHING ASSISTANTS (4 POSITIONS)- CIVIL ENGINEERING&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="field field--name-uid field--type-entity-reference field--label-hidden"&gt;&lt;a title="View user profile." href="https://www.ub.bw/user/1558" lang="" about="https://www.ub.bw/user/1558" typeof="schema:Person" property="schema:name" datatype="" class="username" xml:lang=""&gt;ramahobok&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="field field--name-created field--type-created field--label-hidden"&gt;Mon, 25/07/2022 - 08:30&lt;/span&gt;

  &lt;div class="field field--name-field-department field--type-entity-reference field--label-inline clearfix"&gt;
    &lt;div class="field__label"&gt;Department/Faculty&lt;/div&gt;
              &lt;div class="field__item"&gt;Civil Engineering&lt;/div&gt;
          &lt;/div&gt;

  &lt;div class="field field--name-field-tender-closing-date field--type-datetime field--label-inline clearfix"&gt;
    &lt;div class="field__label"&gt;Closing Date&lt;/div&gt;
              &lt;div class="field__item"&gt;Tue, 9 Aug. 2022&lt;/div&gt;
          &lt;/div&gt;

            &lt;div class="clearfix text-formatted field field--name-body field--type-text-with-summary field--label-hidden field__item"&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;FACULTY OF ENGINEERING AND TECHNOLOGY&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;DEPARTMENT OF CIVIL ENGINEERING&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;PART-TIME TEACHING ASSISTANTS&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;VACANCY &lt;span&gt;NO:  FET/CE04 /2022&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;The Department of Civil Engineering, University of Botswana, is looking for Part-time Teaching   &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Assistants &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;for the academic year &lt;span&gt;2022/2023&lt;/span&gt; in the following areas: Structural Engineering, Geotechnical/Water Engineering and Geomatics.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;Duties&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;:The  successful  applicant will  be  expected to: (i)   assist with tutorials and laboratory practicals, (ii) mark laboratory reports, and (iii) perform&lt;span&gt; any &lt;/span&gt; responsibilities as may be assigned by the Head of Department.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;Requirements:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;S&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;t&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;r&lt;span&gt;u&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;c&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;t&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;u&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;ral Engineering&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span&gt;A&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span&gt;B&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;E&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;g/BSc&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;i&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;n&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;C&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;i&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;v&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;i&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;l&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span&gt;E&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;g&lt;span&gt;i&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;eer&lt;span&gt;i&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;g&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;w&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;i&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;t&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;h&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span&gt;a&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;g&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;ra&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;d&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;e&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span&gt;of &lt;span&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;ii) &lt;span&gt;o&lt;/span&gt;r be&lt;span&gt;t&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;t&lt;/span&gt;er.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;Geotechnical/Water Engineering&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;: A BEng/BSc in Civil Engineering with a grade of 2(ii) &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;or &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;better.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;Geomatics&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;: A BSc in Geomatics/Land Surveying with a grade of 2(ii) or better&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;For all positions, preference will be given to those enrolled in the Department graduate   programmes. Teaching experience will be an added advantage.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;Remuneration:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;As per approved University of Botswana part&lt;span&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;time rates.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;How to apply:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span&gt; Letters of application should demonstrate compliance with the stated requirements and provide any other information to assist the University to determine your suitability for the   position. You should quote the vacancy number of the post applied for, provide current CVs (including telephone, telex and telefax numbers and e-mail), certified true copies   of educational certificates, transcripts and names and addresses of three referees. Send your application to:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;The Human Resources Manager, Faculty of Engineering and Technology, University of Botswana, Private Bag UB 0061, Gaborone. Botswana, Telephone: 267-355 4214. E-mail: &lt;a href="mailto:recruitmentfet@ub.ac.bw"&gt;&lt;span&gt;recruitmentfet@ub.ac.bw&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Applicants should inform their referees to: (i) Quote the Vacancy Number(s) and Position(s) applied for, and (ii) submit their references directly to the above address, before the stipulated closing date.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Hand delivered applications should be submitted to &lt;strong&gt;Office No: 255 Block 248&lt;/strong&gt;. Please note that applications with incomplete&lt;span&gt; i&lt;/span&gt;nformation shall not be considered. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;NB: Only shortlisted applicants will be contacted.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;Closing date: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;9 August 2022&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
